  <entry>
    <title>NoneBot2 新手 FAQ</title>
    <link href="https://mingxuangame.github.io/2022/05/01/NoneBot2-Beginner-FAQ/"/>
    <id>https://mingxuangame.github.io/2022/05/01/NoneBot2-Beginner-FAQ/</id>
    <published>2022-05-01T09:13:22.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-05-01T13:00:31.452Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这里整理了一些新手经常提问的问题，这些问题往往很简单（<a href="https://v2.nonebot.dev/">文档</a>里均有相关内容），但是可能因为某些原因，会导致下面的错误</p><p>下面将根据如下常常提问的问题进行解答</p><h2 id="我要快速精通-Python"><a href="#我要快速精通-Python" class="headerlink" title="我要快速精通 Python"></a>我要快速精通 Python</h2><p>洗洗睡吧，学习都是循序渐进的</p><p>你要是能 3 天精通 Python，为什么不去找工作呢</p><h2 id="有没有通俗易懂的-NoneBot-教程"><a href="#有没有通俗易懂的-NoneBot-教程" class="headerlink" title="有没有通俗易懂的 NoneBot 教程"></a>有没有通俗易懂的 NoneBot 教程</h2><p><a href="http://blog.well404.top/2022/01/30/nonebot/%E3%80%90NoneBot2%E3%80%91%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8NoneBot2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAQQ%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA/">Well404的教程</a></p><h2 id="Bad-Handshake-403"><a href="#Bad-Handshake-403" class="headerlink" title="Bad Handshake(403)"></a>Bad Handshake(403)</h2><p>未注册协议适配器</p><p>相关文档：<a href="https://v2.nonebot.dev/docs/tutorial/register-adapter">使用适配器</a>、<a href="https://onebot.adapters.nonebot.dev/docs/guide/setup/">配置连接</a></p><p>在 <code>bot.py</code> 添加如下代码</p><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>bot.py</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 导入替换为对应的适配器，go-cqhttp 为 OneBot 协议</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> nonebot.adapters.onebot.v11 <span class="keyword">import</span> Adapter</span><br><span class="line">driver.register_adapter(Adapter)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>记得下次在脚手架选中适配器</p><p><img src="/images/cli-select-adapter.png" alt="选择适配器"></p><h2 id="TypeError-Driver-register-adapter-takes-2-positional-arguments-but-3-were-given"><a href="#TypeError-Driver-register-adapter-takes-2-positional-arguments-but-3-were-given" class="headerlink" title="TypeError: Driver.register_adapter() takes 2 positional arguments but 3 were given"></a>TypeError: Driver.register_adapter() takes 2 positional arguments but 3 were given</h2><p>NoneBot2 beta-1 版本修改了注册适配器的方式，需要传入适配器 <code>Adapter</code></p><p>若想使用老版本请在安装时指定</p><p>注册适配器参考上面</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python3 -m pip install nonebot2==2.0.0a16</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="nb-命令未找到"><a href="#nb-命令未找到" class="headerlink" title="nb: 命令未找到"></a>nb: 命令未找到</h2><p>可能是未安装脚手架，或脚手架不在Path中</p><p>相关文档：<a href="https://v2.nonebot.dev/docs/start/nb-cli">使用脚手架</a></p><p>可使用 <code>python3 -m nb_cli</code> 代替</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python3 -m nb_cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="如何发送图片"><a href="#如何发送图片" class="headerlink" title="如何发送图片"></a>如何发送图片</h2><p><strong>发送图片以 OneBot 协议适配器为演示</strong></p><p><strong>麻烦不要使用 CQ 码了</strong></p><p>相关文档：<a href="https://v2.nonebot.dev/docs/tutorial/process-message">处理消息</a>、<a href="https://onebot.adapters.nonebot.dev/docs/api/v11/message#MessageSegment-image">MessageSegment-image</a></p><p>使用 <code>MessageSegment.image</code> 构造图片消息段</p><p>支持 <code>Path</code>、<code>str</code>、<code>BytesIO</code> 和 <code>bytes</code> 类型</p><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>foo/__init__.py</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> io <span class="keyword">import</span> BytesIO</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> pathlib <span class="keyword">import</span> Path</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> nonebot <span class="keyword">import</span> on_message</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> nonebot.adapters.onebot.v11 <span class="keyword">import</span> MessageSegment</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">foo = on_message()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@foo.handle()</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">_</span>():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 当前文件目录的 `img.png` 文件</span></span><br><span class="line">    path = Path(__file__).parent / <span class="string">&quot;img.png&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(path, <span class="string">&quot;rb&quot;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 传入 BytesIO 与 bytes 无异</span></span><br><span class="line">        byte = f.read()  <span class="comment"># type: <span class="built_in">bytes</span></span></span><br><span class="line">        bio = BytesIO(byte)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 以路径形式发送 file:///路径</span></span><br><span class="line">    path_image = MessageSegment.image(path)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 以 base64 发送 base64://</span></span><br><span class="line">    byte_image = MessageSegment.image(byte)</span><br><span class="line">    bio_image = MessageSegment.image(bio)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 以 str 发送，需要填入完整链接</span></span><br><span class="line">    str_image = MessageSegment.image(<span class="string">&quot;https://&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 任选其一发送即可</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">await</span> foo.send(path_image)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="ValidationError"><a href="#ValidationError" class="headerlink" title="ValidationError"></a>ValidationError</h2><p>未填写插件的配置</p><p>请在 <code>.env</code>、<code>.env.dev</code> 或 <code>.env.prod</code> 填写插件的配置</p><p>配置参考插件的文档</p><h2 id="NotImplementedError-且-Traceback-出现-asyncio-字样"><a href="#NotImplementedError-且-Traceback-出现-asyncio-字样" class="headerlink" title="NotImplementedError 且 Traceback 出现 asyncio 字样"></a>NotImplementedError 且 Traceback 出现 <code>asyncio</code> 字样</h2><p>未关闭重载</p><p>相关文档：<a href="https://v2.nonebot.dev/docs/tutorial/choose-driver#fastapi_reload">选择驱动器#fastapi_reload</a></p><p>在配置关闭 <code>fastapi_reload</code> 即可</p><p>也可参考<a href="https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/issues/376#issuecomment-846523618">nonebot&#x2F;nonebot2#376#issuecomment-846523618</a>的猴子补丁修复</p><p>详情参考<a href="https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/issues/376">nonebot&#x2F;nonebot2#376</a>、<a href="https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/issues/830">nonebot&#x2F;nonebot2#830</a></p><h2 id="账号被风控"><a href="#账号被风控" class="headerlink" title="账号被风控"></a>账号被风控</h2><p>tx不开心，把你的机器人风控了（我们称之为喜报）</p><p><img src="/images/can't-send-msg.gif" alt="喜报"></p><p>目前可能解除风控的办法：</p><p>1.切换协议为 MacOS<br>2.使用企业QQ<del>（你不一定能买得起）</del><br><del>3.收购腾讯</del></p><h2 id="Check-your-plugin-name"><a href="#Check-your-plugin-name" class="headerlink" title="Check your plugin name"></a>Check your plugin name</h2><p>插件重复加载，检查 <code>bot.py</code> 和 <code>pyproject.toml</code> 是否已经加载（比如已经在 <code>pyproject.toml</code> 如下设置，请删除 <code>bot.py</code> 的加载代码）</p><figure class="highlight toml"><figcaption><span>pyproject.toml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[tool.nonebot]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">plugins</span> = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">plugin_dirs</span> = [<span class="string">&quot;src/plugins&quot;</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>具体情况因配置而异</p><h2 id="为什么没有-XX-功能"><a href="#为什么没有-XX-功能" class="headerlink" title="为什么没有 XX 功能"></a>为什么没有 XX 功能</h2><p>你去提 <a href="https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/pulls">pr</a> 就有了</p><h2 id="最后"><a href="#最后" class="headerlink" title="最后"></a>最后</h2><p>如果这个文章无法帮到你，请多翻阅<a href="https://v2.nonebot.dev/">文档</a>，那里可能有你想要的答案</p><p>也可通过<a href="https://v2.nonebot.dev/docs/start/question">这些方式</a>提问</p><h3 id="提问前须知"><a href="#提问前须知" class="headerlink" title="提问前须知"></a>提问前须知</h3><p>NoneBot 的文档是免费的，这篇文章也是免费的，没有人从你的手里拿走了一分钱</p><p>请以谦虚的态度提问，并发送相关日志，截图，代码片段</p><p>截图请截取关键点，且尽量完整</p><p><img src="/images/junk-screenshot.jpg" alt="有用的报错你是一行没截到.jpg"></p><p><strong>建议阅读<a href="https://github.com/ryanhanwu/How-To-Ask-Questions-The-Smart-Way/blob/main/README-zh_CN.md">提问的智慧</a></strong></p><h2 id="给这篇文章提供更多-FAQ"><a href="#给这篇文章提供更多-FAQ" class="headerlink" title="给这篇文章提供更多 FAQ"></a>给这篇文章提供更多 FAQ</h2><p>请通过 <a href="https://github.com/MingxuanGame/mingxuangame.github.io/issues">Issue</a> 附带 <code>FAQ</code> 标签提建议</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
